==English==
===Noun===
(''grammatical terminology''): [[case]] used to indicate movement onto, or to the [[adjacent|adjacency]] of something. In English, this is usually expressed by the prepositions "to" or "onto," as in "to the house," "onto the house." Languages that use the allative case include [[Dyirbal]][, [Finnish]], [[Hungarian]], [[Estonian]], and [[Lithuanian]].

